e-x.56.x","Navigating Settings Presents Error When you Select Auth or Embedding Sections","docs - note on pinning","Add documentation for password settings on Metabase Cloud","docs - clarify JWT Identity Provider URI instructions","Manual backport of preserving table whitespaces changes","Postgres queries fail with `java.lang.Class.isArray()` errors after upgrade to v0.56.3","A caret cursor is not visible in filter inputs","Content layout shift when checking an item in a collection","Pivot table export outputs blank values when pivoting on integer columns","Auto-update documentation for release-x.56.x","Better branch detection if relevant files are changed for CI","Fix flaky UpdatesNavItem test","Update Debian/systemd docs","Fix references to pre-56 Troubleshooting admin menu","Drill through no longer works for pivot tables in the latest version","Fix flaky test for metabase-browser custom element","Card filters seem to be avoiding the linkage to dashboard filters","Discard cached field values will... refresh the values?","Fix tabs alignment for horizontal tabs with grow (#61895)","docs: translations limitations","skip flaky loki row chart tests","There are more selected columns than there are total columns","refactor(sdk): Rename embedding-sdk directory to embedding-sdk-bundle","chore: upgrade vulnerable cipher-base package","chore: upgrade vulnerable sha.js package","[BOT-316] Metabase BE support for dynamic agent profiles","Respond with HTTP status 500 when Store API request fails during Cloud migration","fix(sdk): Add background-light to derived colors for the new embed","Content Translation doesn't translate pivot table columns","publicly-shared dashboards show blank pages when viewed in incognito (or by non-authenticated users)","[Metabot] Add `available_actions` to metabot context","Download button overlaps table header with embedding title is not enabled.","Cannot assign certain column types to fields in models","[QP] Don't apply `:coercion-strategy` to join